{"tid":1560470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】化學工程師衝突現場取樣本　證催淚煙化學物可殘留達3周","createTime":"2019-09-11T08:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T08:24:16.000Z","uid":53379,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ae8dc59d7879fd2f62223889ee1f641091e1c1a1","tid":1560470,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:06:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【逃犯條例】化學工程師衝突現場取樣本　證催淚煙化學物可殘留達3周</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n反修訂《逃犯條例》風波至今觸發多場警民衝突，警方自6月起發放逾2000枚催淚彈。一批化學工程師在衝突現場收集樣本研究催淚煙在社區殘留情况，發現催淚煙中引致不適的化學成分CS，可殘留在環境中達兩至三星期。<br />\n<br />\n該團隊在8月18日起，在金鐘、上環、西營盤、九龍灣、深水埗及荃灣，收集200多個物件表面的塵埃樣本作分析。化學工程師李浩基表示，8月18日在上環及西營盤收集樣本後，仍能偵測出CS化學物，而追溯該區上一次放催淚彈已是7月28日，即21日前；他說，警方強調催淚彈殘留時間不長，與其研究結果不符。<br />\n<br />\n李浩基又表示，研究推斷在空氣流通的地方，催淚煙的影響範圍更廣。他舉例，警方在荃灣楊屋道施放催淚彈當日，團隊在直線距離250米外荃灣公園一處單車橋底偵測出CS化學物，但在河背街及眾安街等較窄的街道，礙於空氣不流通而未受影響。他擔心，由於化學物未能以肉眼認出，如有兒童在遊樂場接觸到受影響設施，會影響健康。<br />\n<br />\n李浩基承認是次研究未能測出殘留化學物濃度，亦礙於人手有限未能持續研究，故促請政府檢測受催淚彈影響範圍，並徹底清潔，保障市民安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190911/s00001/1568178753707/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e5%8c%96%e5%ad%b8%e5%b7%a5%e7%a8%8b%e5%b8%ab%e8%a1%9d%e7%aa%81%e7%8f%be%e5%a0%b4%e5%8f%96%e6%a8%a3%e6%9c%ac-%e8%ad%89%e5%82%ac%e6%b7%9a%e7%85%99%e5%8c%96%e5%ad%b8%e7%89%a9%e5%8f%af%e6%ae%98%e7%95%99%e9%81%943%e5%91%a8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190911%2Fs00001%2F1568178753707%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%258c%2596%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e7%25a8%258b%25e5%25b8%25ab%25e8%25a1%259d%25e7%25aa%2581%25e7%258f%25be%25e5%25a0%25b4%25e5%258f%2596%25e6%25a8%25a3%25e6%259c%25ac-%25e8%25ad%2589%25e5%2582%25ac%25e6%25b7%259a%25e7%2585%2599%25e5%258c%2596%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e7%2589%25a9%25e5%258f%25af%25e6%25ae%2598%25e7%2595%2599%25e9%2581%25943%25e5%2591%25a8&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=34a8d323\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190911%2Fs00001%2F1568178753707%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%258c%2596%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e7%25a8%258b%25e5%25b8%25ab%25e8%25a1%259d%25e7%25aa%2581%25e7%258f%25be%25e5%25a0%25b4%25e5%258f%2596%25e6%25a8%25a3%25e6%259c%25ac-%25e8%25ad%2589%25e5%2582%25ac%25e6%25b7%259a%25e7%2585%2599%25e5%258c%2596%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e7%2589%25a9%25e5%258f%25af%25e6%25ae%2598%25e7%2595%2599%25e9%2581%25943%25e5%2591%25a8&h=a111b7d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190911/s00001/1568178753707/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e5%8c%96%e5%ad%b8%e5%b7%a5%e7%a8%8b%e5%b8%ab%e8%a1%9d%e7%aa%81%e7%8f%be%e5%a0%b4%e5%8f%96%e6%a8%a3%e6%9c%ac-%e8%ad%89%e5%82%ac%e6%b7%9a%e7%85%99%e5%8c%96%e5%ad%b8%e7%89%a9%e5%8f%af%e6%ae%98%e7%95%99%e9%81%943%e5%91%a8</a>"},{"pid":"d5c05a5f5303213c4e6912026fcf96248525c2d0","tid":1560470,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:09:29.000Z","msg":"[多圖高清] [不廢up] 一人一文宣行動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560411</a>"},{"pid":"87fa00e3a524d76db94ebb7b4749155fea41ac65","tid":1560470,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e177ebb58e654f70d7ae03b30350c7f7ba4eb829","tid":1560470,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:20:02.000Z","msg":"終於做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c49905c5dbe